  "text": "Assessment of the reliability was confirmed by looking at the peak stress (von Mises) inside model parts as shown in Table 3 . Using failure stress data of 48 and 493 MPa for the pledget and suture respectively [CITATION_1] ASM International, 2009 ), we assessed that stresses remain in the elastic domain for the elastic parts.",
